approve(address,uint256).notice: Allow spender to access an amount of your eTokens in sub-account 0

approveSubAccount(uint256,address,uint25.notice: Allow spender to access an amount of your eTokens in a particular sub-account

balanceOf(address).notice: Balance of a particular account, in internal book-keeping units (non-increasing)

balanceOfUnderlying(address).notice: Balance of a particular account, in underlying units (increases as interest is earned)

burn(uint256,uint256).notice: Pay off dToken liability with eTokens ("self-repay")

convertBalanceToUnderlying(uint256).notice: Convert an eToken balance to an underlying amount, taking into account current exchange rate

convertUnderlyingToBalance(uint256).notice: Convert an underlying amount to an eToken balance, taking into account current exchange rate

deposit(uint256,uint256).notice: Transfer underlying tokens from sender to the Euler pool, and increase account's eTokens

mint(uint256,uint256).notice: Mint eTokens and a corresponding amount of dTokens ("self-borrow")

reserveBalance().notice: Balance of the reserves, in internal book-keeping units (non-increasing)

reserveBalanceUnderlying().notice: Balance of the reserves, in underlying units (increases as interest is earned)

totalSupply().notice: Sum of all balances, in internal book-keeping units (non-increasing)

totalSupplyUnderlying().notice: Sum of all balances, in underlying units (increases as interest is earned)

touch().notice: Updates interest accumulator and totalBorrows, credits reserves, re-targets interest rate, and logs asset status

transfer(address,uint256).notice: Transfer eTokens to another address (from sub-account 0)

transferFrom(address,address,uint256).notice: Transfer eTokens from one address to another

transferFromMax(address,address).notice: Transfer the full eToken balance of an address to another

withdraw(uint256,uint256).notice: Transfer underlying tokens from Euler pool to sender, and decrease account's eTokens
